{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1699607289.368726", "card_id": "Q_629699666", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 283}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "报告称超 9 成回国留学生面临求职压力，专家建议「留学生降低薪资期待」，如何看待此事？留学还有必要吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近年来，越来越多的留学生选择归国就业。但留学生回国就业的压力也不小。《2023 海外留学人才就业发展报告》显示，在打算回国就业的留学生中，超九成面临求职压力，排名前三的原因分别为：「国内优秀人才越来越多，岗位有限，就业竞争激烈」、「留学花费很多，担心薪资不达预期，很难回本」、「海归人数持续增加，其优势已不如以前突出」。 由于留学成本高，该群体对薪资期望也更高。大学生实习校招平台实习僧 CEO 曾舒煜称，国内 985 应届毕业生的平均起薪期望约 0.8 万 -1.2 万元，英美留学应届生的期望薪资则在一万至一万五间，曾舒煜建议，留学生应适当降低薪资期待。 懒就业、慢就业，海归如何走出求职之困？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-533990904fbe19e51bf0bc4ad2801ae7_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1100 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/629699666"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIr/nwtLrM3KIWEAMaCTEwMjIxMTc1MSDwj7aqBjAAOJgEQAByCTYyOTY5OTY2NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1699607289.369951", "card_id": "Q_268227369", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 252}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么好多学校都喜欢挖个湖？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ecfb46ba6a5f3721df91550f641adb57_xl.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "626 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/268227369"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ir/nwtLrM3KIWEAMaCDIxNzI0MjA4ILDJ89QFMAA4+ANAAXIJMjY4MjI3MzY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1699607289.370400", "card_id": "Q_576349950", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_144